<c74object name='av.pix.tiltblur' category='' module=''>

    <digest>
        Apply a tilt-blur effect
    </digest>

    <description>
        Apply a gaussian tilt-blur effect. The tiltblur has either a circular, vertical or horizontal shape. You can change the blur amount, the width of the focus and the edge fade from no-blur into the blurred area of the image. A common used technique to apply some depth-of-field and focus to a 2D image.
    </description>
    
    <discussion>
        
    </discussion>

